Could not figure out a way to say this without seeming to be bragging, but lets go for it anyway.

I drove the Nürburgring with a Donkervoort D8 GTO, which was much more car then i ever should have handled. Lots of fun but damn it was terrifying. I went with my dad and we bought 4 laps, 2 each, but only did 1 each since we decided that we were lucky not to crash in the first lap
